Yeah, well life is life. I lit someones hair on fire friday in school. SO this means I have 5 days OSS. I probably wont be able to go to prom. And may not be able to graduate either. Oh well. What can I do. Thats just my luck. Yeah so once again shit hit the fan with someone. And once again, I hadda clean it up. The fan is clean now, for now. but as I have learned in the past that can change in an instant. This weekend was better than any I've had in a long long long time. I got to chill with someone everyday this weekend. It was great. Today I went to her dance competition, I didnt get to see any of her routines, but I saw her get her medals and stuff. It was nice. I dunno. I'm jus not in one of the best moods, I guess its because no matter how hard I try, I can never get things good enough in her life to be acceptable, and make her happy. She lets her family and what not bring her down way too much. I cant wait till the day she finally realizes, that she really is beautiful and she really is a great person, and that I love her more than anyone on earth. One day she'll see. Thats my goal in life. To make sure she knows how great she really is, and that there is more to life than her problems and setbacks. blah. I dunno. I jus wanna sleep. I really do. I wanna go to bed with her and wake up again when we are like 25. And we'll have good jobs and start a family. I needa go. I love you Dork!
